OL,3,CUrgent tests missed before dad's
OL,4,Ccardiac death in hospital
OL,6,FThe mother of a man who suffered a
OL,7,Ffatal cardiac arrest after a series of
OL,8,Fmistakes in hospital says she is
OL,9,F"bitter and angry".
OL,11,FA coroner said there were "missed
OL,12,Fopportunities" to save father-of-one
OL,13,FLee Stammers, 47, before he died
OL,14,Fwithin hours of being admitted to
OL,15,FDoncaster Royal Infirmary (DRI).
OL,17,FMr Stammers' mother, Sheila, of
OL,18,FSprotbrough, Doncaster, said her son's
OL,19,Fchances of survival had been
OL,20,Fundermined.
