OL,3,CUrgent tests missed before dad's
OL,4,Ccardiac death in hospital
OL,6,F"I am very bitter and angry because of
OL,7,Fso many missed opportunities and
OL,8,Fmistakes," she said.
OL,10,F"He could have had a chance of
OL,11,Fsurvival if he had been managed
OL,12,Fdifferently."
OL,14,FMr Stammers was treated for an
OL,15,Finfection after presenting at DRI with
OL,16,Fchest pains, shortness of breath and
OL,17,Fnausea on 10 February.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
