OL,3,CUrgent tests missed before dad's
OL,4,Ccardiac death in hospital
OL,6,FBut South Yorkshire coroner Louise
OL,7,FSlater said there were medics failed
OL,8,Fto identify a heart condition called
OL,9,Fmyocardial ischemia.
OL,11,FAn ECG test was incomplete, not
OL,12,Freported and was not repeated and
OL,13,Fblood tests were not performed as
OL,14,Frequested.
OL,16,F"Inaccurate information in the medical
OL,17,Frecords and poor communication led to
OL,18,Fa failure of urgent tests being
OL,19,Fundertaken," Ms Slater said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
