OL,6,FThe coroner said Mr Stammers may have
OL,7,Fhad a better chance of survival had
OL,8,Fthe tests been done, although it was
OL,9,Fnot possible to determine if he would
OL,10,Fhave avoided cardiac arrest.
OL,12,F'Clear evidence of poor documentation'
OL,14,FIn a Prevention of Future Deaths
OL,15,Freport, the coroner highlighted "poor
OL,16,Fdocumentation, communications and
OL,17,Fsystems".
OL,19,FMedical records wrongly indicated that
OL,20,Fblood had been obtained and collected
OL,21,Fby the laboratory.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
