OL,3,CUrgent tests missed before dad's
OL,4,Ccardiac death in hospital
OL,6,FThere were similar problems with a
OL,7,Flack of communication about the ECG,
OL,8,Fwhich "allowed tests/actions to be
OL,9,Fcancelled by student nurses, temporary
OL,10,Fstaff and locum clinicians, who can
OL,11,Falso access the system and cancel
OL,12,Ftests without any rationale", the
OL,13,Fcoroner said.
OL,15,F"Finally, there was clear and
OL,16,Fconsistent evidence of poor
OL,17,Fdocumentation throughout the medical
OL,18,Frecords, from admission to the
OL,19,Femergency department continuing
OL,20,Fthrough to the resuscitation attempts."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
