OL,6,FIn a statement, Dr Nick Mallaband,
OL,7,Facting executive medical director at
OL,8,FDRI, said: "We would like to extend
OL,9,Four sincere condolences to the family,
OL,10,Ffriends and loved ones of Mr Stammers
OL,11,Fat this very difficult time.
OL,13,F"Following this case, we have
OL,14,Fidentified a number of areas where
OL,15,Fimprovements were required.
OL,17,F"These changes have now been
OL,18,Fimplemented within our emergency
OL,19,Fdepartment.
